snippet.title: Shaky ( Official #Video ) Sanju Rathod Ft. Isha Malviya | G-Spark | New #Marathi Songs 2025
snippet.description:
Provided To Youtube By Amal Star Media
| üïâ ||
Sanju Rathod presents 'Shaky' a Marathi track like no other!

Shaky is a fresh Marathi Pop anthem that blends playful Afrobeat grooves with everyday desi charm. Sanju Rathod and Isha Malviya bring effortless swag, catchy hooks, and vibrant energy in this fun, feel-good love track. A bold, danceable vibe that pushes Marathi music into exciting new territory.

Singer - Sanju Rathod
LyricsComposer - Sanju Rathod
Music Produced By - G-Spark
Vocal Production Mixed By - G-Spark
Additional Mix Mastered By - Rupendar Venkatesh @mixmagic Studios

snippet.title: Mowgli Trailer | Roshan Kanakala | Bandi Saroj Kumar | Sandeep Raj | Sakkshi | TG Vishwa Prasad
snippet.description:
Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Mowgli is an upcoming 2025 unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

snippet.title: Jaliba Mo Jui || Prem Darshan || Pushpa || Humane Sagar || Odia Music Video || Enewsodia
snippet.description:
üíî ‚ÄúAji Rati Gale Pahi Jaliba Mo Jui‚Äù is a heart-touching Odia sad song that reflects the pain of separation, unspoken feelings, and emotional heartbreak sang by Humane Sagar. The soulful voice and emotional lyrics beautifully bring out the depth of love that has been lost, making this track relatable for anyone who has experienced sadness in love.The song captures the journey of someone who still cherishes their beloved (Jui ‚Äì meaning the light of life) even after distance and destiny have created a painful gap. Its melody, music arrangement, and emotional expression make it a powerful sad song that stays with listeners long after it ends.

Cast : Prem Darshan & Pushpa
Director : Smruti.R

Duniaru chalijibi nathiba mo chai nathibi mo chai
Kanhiki jinbi kanhiki rahibi nija saba nije bohi
Jahara tu jahara tu delu pei jinthai masanire delu soi[2]
delu soi delu soi

tate khusi debi boli mo khusi bhuli thili
 tate rani karithilii mu pache dukhare thili
hrudayaku delu dali jibanaku delu dali
biswasare bisa dei mo premare delu dhuli
kanhiki bhabibi kanhiki kandibi adheidiniaa pain
Jahara tu jahara tu delu pei jinthai masanire delu soi[2]
delu soi delu soi

fula jebe magithilu kanta sahi deithili
janha jebe magithilu chanda toil deithili
nakari aaji mu dosa karidelu mate dosi
chalanara rasi dhari deidelu mate fasi
kanhiki jitibi kanhiki haribi alapa samaya pain
Jahara tu jahara tu delu pei jinthai masanire delu soi[2]
delu soi delu soi

On the auspicious occasion of Shri Datta Jayanti, we present the soulful and divine Dattatreya Aarti, sung by the melodious Prathamesh Laghate, only on Tips Bhakti Prem.
 Immerse yourself in devotion as this powerful Marathi Aarti praises Lord Dattatreya, the divine embodiment of Brahma, Vishnu, and Mahesh.

About Lord Dattatreya
Lord Dattatreya is revered as the combined incarnation of Brahma, Vishnu, and Mahesh, symbolizing creation, preservation, and dissolution. Considered the Adi Guru (the original spiritual master), he embodies ultimate knowledge, detachment, and inner freedom.
 Devotees believe that worshipping Lord Datta removes fears, resolves karmic obstacles, guides the seeker on the path of truth, and grants protection and blessings.

About Datta Jayanti
Datta Jayanti marks the divine birth of Lord Dattatreya and is celebrated with deep devotion. On this day, devotees chant Datta Stotras, read Guru Charitra, perform prayers, and seek spiritual guidance from the Lord of the Three Worlds.
Immerse yourself in this powerful aarti and invoke the blessings of Shri Gurudatta.

To receive regular updates on devotional songs subscribe to us on the following link: https://www.youtube.com/BhaktiPrem

On the auspicious occasion of Shri Datta Jayanti, we present the soulful and divine Dattatreya Aarti, sung by the melodious Prathamesh Laghate, only on Tips Bhakti Prem.
 Immerse yourself in devotion as this powerful Marathi Aarti praises Lord Dattatreya, the divine embodiment of Brahma, Vishnu, and Mahesh.

About Lord Dattatreya
Lord Dattatreya is revered as the combined incarnation of Brahma, Vishnu, and Mahesh, symbolizing creation, preservation, and dissolution. Considered the Adi Guru (the original spiritual master), he embodies ultimate knowledge, detachment, and inner freedom.
 Devotees believe that worshipping Lord Datta removes fears, resolves karmic obstacles, guides the seeker on the path of truth, and grants protection and blessings.

About Datta Jayanti
Datta Jayanti marks the divine birth of Lord Dattatreya and is celebrated with deep devotion. On this day, devotees chant Datta Stotras, read Guru Charitra, perform prayers, and seek spiritual guidance from the Lord of the Three Worlds.
Immerse yourself in this powerful aarti and invoke the blessings of Shri Gurudatta.

To receive regular updates on devotional songs subscribe to us on the following link: https://www.youtube.com/BhaktiPrem

snippet.title: Chann Sitare | Ammy Virk | Tania | Simerjit Singh | Avvy Sra | Oye Makhna
snippet.description:
You asked for it again! The love anthem ‚ÄòChann Sitare‚Äô from Oye Makhna, sung by Ammy Virk, is back to melt your hearts all over again.

Audio Credits:
Singer - Ammy Virk
Composer - Harmanjeet Singh,Avvy Sra
Lyrics - Harmanjeet Singh
Guitars - Shomu Seal

Movie Credits:
Movie: Oye Makhna  
Directed By: Simerjit Singh
Written By: Rakesh Dhawan
Produced By: Vikram Mehra, Siddharth Anand Kumar, Simerjit Singh, Ammy Virk
Co-producer: Sahil Sharma
Executive Producer: Alok Batra, Aashish Mehra, Anurodh Gusain, Akshay Valsangkar
Creative Producer: Manoj Sabharwal, Abhijit Deb
Line Producer: Manmeet Singh Ohson
Associate Director : Gadar 
Chief Assistant Director : Sanjeev Arora
Editor : Anurodh Gusain
Starring: Ammy Virk, Guggu Gill, Tania, Sidhika Sharma
Cast: Sukhwinder Chahal, Hardeep Gill, Tarsem Paul, Deedar Gill,satwant Kaur, Rose J. Kaur, Manju Mahal, Parminder Gill
Dop: Sandeep Patil

Video Credits:
Music: Avvy Sra
Background Music: Inder Bawra, Sunny Bawra
Story By: Rakesh Dhawan
Screenplay: Rakesh Dhawan
Dialogue: Rakesh Dhawan
Financial Controller: Gurdeep Singh Saskaur
Choreographer: Ritchie Burton
Production Design: Saurabh Kaushk
Chief Assistant Director: Anil  Sharma, Sachin Arora 
Costume Stylist :  Roma Sharma
Makeup: Pradeep Kumar 
Sound Design: Vijaykumar, Mpse
Di Colourist: Sameer Pandit
Subtitles: Digital Nirvana Films
Music On: Saregama

All Mix Mastered By Yograj Singh And Suyash Singh At Mix N Vibe Studios
Assistant Music Producer And Sound Designer : Jaydden
 
Lyrics:
Jo pichale dina to tak reha,eh chehra khore kisda ai
Jo hor kite mainu labbiyan ni tere naina vichon disda ai
Nadi cheel ya parbat hai ya koi khazana khaaban da 
Tere naina vicho jhalak reha koi rang sunehrean
Baggan da
Tu ek chutki maari unglan di,mai tenu jhal marunga pakhiyan nal 
Mai chann sitaare ki karne mainu ishq ho gaya 
Akhiyan nal
Mainu ishq ho gaya akhiyan nal

Ek taar khardi rehndi hai mai sham savere sunda han
Kikran deyan peleyan phoola nu,mai kalan beh beh
Chundan han
mai kalan beh beh Chundan han
mai phool tere pairi rakh deyun
tu jad lagna aapni sakhiyan nal
Mai chann sitaare ki karne mainu ishq ho gaya 
Akhiyan nal
Mainu ishq ho gaya akhiyan nal

snippet.description:
Wassup Gamers,

Today I will be playing a game where my angry wife/girlfriend threw out my valuable items in the garbage dump outside and I have to go find them. A cozy garbage-cleaning simulator. Dig through the dump, find ultra-rare collectible cards, rescue tangled birds, and relax.

Follow Me On EVERYWHERE! *Not on streets please :')*
